Steps to create a plot about the element types that are given as a list in summary.txt

1) copy only the element types list from summary.txt to a single file
2) run: perl table4Types.pl typelist typetable.tab
3) start R:

> x = read.table("element_types.tab",sep="\t",header=T)
> tmp_rows = x[,1]
> x = x[,2:ncol(x)]
> rownames(x) = tmp_rows
> x3 = apply(x,2,as.numeric)
> rownames(x3) = tmp_rows
> pdf("barplot_elementTypesPerSpecies.pdf")
> barplot(x3, main = "Number of Elements per Species", col = c("blue","red","orange","green","black","cyan"), legend = rownames(x3),las=2, xlab = "Element Types", ylab = "Number of Elements")
> dev.off()